Atualizar nodejs e npm
Instalar a CLI do Angular

npm install -g @angular/CLI
ng new <nome da aplicacao>
cd <nome da aplicacao>
ng serve

npm install --save bootstrap
    ../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css
        Dentro de 'styles', .angular-cli.json

Angular roda main.ts, e lá vai carregando os módulos, etc.

ng generate component servers
    ng g c servers